    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical heartbeat is strong, with a recently serviced VANOS system ensuring optimal variable valve timing across the power band. Critical subframe reinforcement has been completed to manage the chassis's torsional loads, a must-have for this platform. The drivetrain is rounded out by a factory limited-slip differential and a refreshed cooling system. Suspension geometry remains precise thanks to updated bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. It\u2019s a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s peak naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 33500.0,
