      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly balances performance with daily reliability. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though it does show minor, age-appropriate signs of use such as light stone chipping on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel. The interior is a highlight\u2014completely smoke-free and professionally detailed, featuring leather seats that remain firm and supportive, with only minor creasing on the driver's side bolster. All onboard electronics, including the infotainment system, navigation, and heated seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth power, backed by a complete service history and a recent oil change. The brakes are responsive, and the tires currently have approximately 70% tread life remaining. This car has been driven thoughtfully and maintained with an open checkbook, making it a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready to drive home today.",
